  "text": "is an integrable function for every X \u2208 R 3d , \u03b1 = (\u03b1 1 , \u03b1 2 , \u03b1 3 ) \u2208 N 3d , and \u03b2 = (\u03b2 1 , \u03b2 2 , \u03b2 3 ) \u2208 N 3d in view of [CITATION_1] . Hence the derivatives of a in (2.7) satisfy the following estimates:",
